## CSS Selectors

- **Rule**
  - selector and declaration combined.
  - ![css selector](img/css_selector.png)
- **Selector**
  - the 'tag' name.
  - ![css selector](img/css_selector.png)
- **Declaration**
  - everything inside the brackets.
  - ![css selector](img/css_selector.png)
- **Property and Value**
  - css attributes inside the brackets.
  - ![css selector](img/css_selector.png)
- **External CSS**
  - link to css file.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="mystyle.css" />
  </head>
  <body></body>
</html>
```
